{"tid":366531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台：現時室外氣溫35度，應避免在陽光下曝曬","createTime":"2017-08-20T05:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T06:20:10.000Z","uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c12fb8de59c4b40a74033014d1981c1bd9e003c6","tid":366531,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"酷熱天氣警告<br />\n<br />\n現時氣溫35 度，酷熱天氣警告現正生效。天文台預料未來一兩日本港天氣酷熱，加上風勢輕微，市民應提高警惕，以防中暑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n避免在陽光下曝曬，以免受太陽紫外線曬傷。應穿上鬆身衣服以及配戴適當帽子和能阻隔紫外線的太陽眼鏡。"},{"pid":"ed11366a8d1a81f2d0ca7bfeff67004ee4b1fccf","tid":366531,"uid":42407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"e10a0899a35bed5a8a2fc1fefea399a20a5b5b1d","tid":366531,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T06:02:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d5136a10ce50afe1bfd6d1ca6f36e634d140e17","tid":366531,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T06:20:10.000Z","msg":"想鼓吹人去邊度避暑呀樓豬"}]}